{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-01809/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-01809"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:18:09"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["dirty single"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman and man sit at a table in an empty restaurant."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-01809","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-01809"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1/a07095ea-5b46-4d35-a644-7b76a00636d8","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T15:05:44.584Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma’s red dress matches the red lampshades and flowers on the table and in the background. Her dynamism populates the space and contrasts with the more mellow golden light of the larger lamp in the corner of the room, not to mention Reynolds’s somber black and gray outfit.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1560.5726872246696,146.2885462555065,344.7136563876652,872.0484581497799"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1/916a2fc4-433c-4439-bb1d-17f327d37922","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T15:05:58.845Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The dress Alma wears features a row of buttons on the front seemingly for purely decorative purposes, as they appear sewn on rather than buttoned in. The dress looks quite visibly cheap—several of the buttons seem to be only loosely sewn in, hanging at strange angles. This seemingly thoughtless design choice a far cry from the beauty and craftsmanship of the clothes Reynolds makes.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01809/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1040.8700440528632,567.8193832599118,82.8854625550664,330.25330396475783"}}}]}]}]}